      "message": "We should probably do something like:\nc.Score \u003d CANDIDATE_SCORE_TRY_JOB + now.Sub(c.Job.Created).Hours()\nThis ensures that try jobs that have been waiting longer are scheduled first.\n\nProbably should do the same for IsForceRun().\n\nMight be easier to add a JobBaseScore field to taskCandidate so we can set it in findTaskCandidatesForJobs.",
