      "message": "I\u0027m thinking it will be more fault-tolerant to add new Jobs to the DB immediately when manually triggered, and just change JobCache.ScheduledJobsForCommit to return false if the jobs weren\u0027t auto-generated for a commit.\n\nIt might be easiest for try jobs to work the same way.",
