      "message": "I should add expiration to jobCache. We ought to expire jobs (i.e. s.jCache.Update()) before calling updateUnfinishedJobs(); if not, the job\u0027s dependent tasks may have already expired, causing us to set an erroneous job status. (This is pretty unlikely, since the only way this would happen is if a task completed *just* before expiring from the cache.)",
